1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,759
Could it be...

4
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,000
My Lady,

5
00:01:00,679 --> 00:01:02,039
you know everything?

6
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,040
I've already figured it out.

7
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:06,599
The man who kept you out all night

8
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,400
is Mo Shuo.

9
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,400
He brought this for you last night.

10
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:16,959
Indeed.

11
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:18,920
This was

12
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,040
the one I liked yesterday.

13
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,400
I didn't expect Mo Shuo
to keep his word.

14
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,719
It's good to meet someone you like,

15
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:29,079
just as described
in Fantasy of the Red Chamber.

16
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:30,359
And you, My Lady?

17
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,799
Do you have someone in your heart?

18
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,400
Why does my heart race

19
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:42,159
so differently whenever I think of him?

20
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,159
His background is unknown.

21
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:45,519
Don't trust so easily.

22
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:48,120
But why does he feel so familiar?

23
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:49,680
Doesn't every relationship

24
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,799
start with a leap of faith?

25
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,520
Mo Shuo.

26
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,840
Ling Xiao is out of danger now.

27
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,439
He's resting at the inn.

28
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:17,840
I've been thinking

29
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,000
that we give them a chance,

30
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,240
and ourselves too.

31
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,280
I thought you wouldn't come.

32
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,759
Then why are you here waiting for me?

33
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,919
Because when it comes to
waiting for you,

34
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,599
I have perseverance and talent.

35
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,439
How did you know

36
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,360
I would definitely come here?

37
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,599
I'm betting on it.

38
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,479
I've thought about it, dreamed about it,

39
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:49,599
and pictured it countless times

40
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:51,319
that you climbed over the palace walls

41
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,639
in your night clothes

42
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,800
and pressed a sword to my throat.

43
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,800
But that day was different.

44
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,360
It was the Qixi Festival.

45
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,639
I truly wanted to spend it with you.

46
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,560
And I won my bet.

47
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,960
I just realized

48
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,240
that you hadn't stood me up.

49
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,719
This is for you.

50
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,520
What is it?

51
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,280
Last time you saw this sword,

52
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,120
but you didn't buy it.

53
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:27,919
Show this token

54
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,240
to any money changer in the city,

55
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,520
and they will give you some silver.

56
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:34,120
I don't want to be in your debt.

57
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,039
The truth is, I'm the one in your debt.

58
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,120
Trying to buy your way out?

59
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,199
In your dreams.

60
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:45,800
Then I'll repay you with love and action

61
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,159
to make it up.

62
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,360
Hungry?

63
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,800
I made grilled chicken wings for you,
your favorite.

64
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,520
Smells so good!

65
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,120
Delicious!

66
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:10,960
Take one.

67
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,039
They're all for you.

68
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,240
Really?

69
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,280
You might regret that!

70
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,759
Mu Ruyi,

71
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,519
I miss you so much.

72
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,800
I'm right here by your side!

73
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,959
Mu Ruyi...

74
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,319
Liuli...

75
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,639
Jing Liuli...

76
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:33,759
Don't leave me...

77
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:36,600
- Come back to me...
- Who are you talking about?

78
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,360
Please come back...

79
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:43,040
Answer me! Who!

80
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,399
Who else are you thinking about?

81
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,879
Is Xia Ke'er right about you?

82
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:55,279
Do you really have an unknown

83
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,000
and dangerous past?

84
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,519
My Lady,

85
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:18,240
you are drinking too much!

86
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:23,199
Mu Ruyi this, Mu Ruyi that...

87
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,639
I'll be Mu Ruyi the Third!

88
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,439
And Jing Liuli?

89
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,639
Liuli this, Liuli that...

90
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:31,959
My Lady, who told you about these names?

91
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:35,600
Last night, he kept calling out

92
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,120
these names in his dream!

93
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,959
Two different women!

94
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,560
These names

95
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,720
sound like they're from the brothels.

96
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,000
Don't dwell on it.

97
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,040
Brothels?

98
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:52,079
So he pretends to be devoted
and innocent,

99
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,519
but he turns out to be

100
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:55,720
a playboy?

101
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,920
Am I not as good as Ruyi

102
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,079
or Liuli?

103
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,720
My Lady, is he that important to you?

104
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:04,360
I must get to the bottom of this.

105
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,480
He's not going to fool me!

106
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:07,800
But what if the truth you uncover

107
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,480
isn't what you want to hear?

108
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,279
What if it hurts you?

109
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:17,279
Let the old make way for the new.

110
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,560
We part ways now.

111
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,079
I'll rough him up to feel better

112
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,000
and never see him again.

113
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,000
If you can truly be so carefree,

114
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,399
then nothing could be better.

115
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:42,839
Rushi,

116
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,519
you've been drinking too much!

117
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,879
Who are you? Let go of me!

118
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,079
What's wrong?

119
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,319
Everything was fine
between us yesterday.

120
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:53,519
Then do you know my name?

121
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,160
Stop it.

122
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,360
Let's go home.

123
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,240
Do you have any memory

124
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,639
of what you said to me last night?

125
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:00,800
Last night?

126
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,000
No.

127
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,439
Maybe I should ask

128
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,959
what you were muttering in your sleep

129
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:10,120
to Mu Ruyi and Jing Liuli,

130
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,439
the ones you've been dreaming of.

131
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,800
Who are they? I don't know.

132
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,720
Then answer this.

133
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,720
Is Mo Shuo your real name?

134
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,199
Rushi,

135
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,959
I can explain that.

136
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,279
Mo Shuo was the one
who saved you that night.

137
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,319
You're his brother,

138
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:34,439
and you often use his name
to flirt with others.

139
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,199
Up until now,

140
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:39,240
I don't even know your real name.

141
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,199
Ling Xiao.

142
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,639
My name is Ling Xiao.

143
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,439
If you trusted me,

144
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,839
you would have been honest with me
from the start.

145
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,000
Leave!

146
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,360
I don't want to see you.

147
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,959
Fine, I'll leave!

148
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,720
You've ruined a perfectly good game
of Go.

149
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,560
What a pity.

150
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,839
Why did you give away my identity

151
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,879
to Liu Rushi?

152
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,680
Why do you care so much about Liu Rushi?

153
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,759
I just do,

154
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,240
it's none of your business.

155
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,519
Given that,

156
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,199
I've brought you both so openly,

157
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,839
you should be grateful.

158
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,519
Openly?

159
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,840
Then tell me,

160
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:35,919
who are Mu Ruyi and Jing Liuli?

161
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:37,320
And what do they have to do with me?

162
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,039
How do you know about them?

163
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,279
I won't trust you again.

164
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,399
I'll uncover the truth myself

165
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:47,000
if I want to.

166
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,440
Your Majesty!

167
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,360
Don't follow me!

168
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,600
Mu Ruyi,

169
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,080
former princess of the previous dynasty,

170
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:13,159
died at the age of 20.

171
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,399
Jing Liuli.

172
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:24,120
She was titled Consort Li
upon entering the palace

173
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:27,840
and was later promoted to
the Noble Consort.

174
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:31,480
Sheng.

175
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,240
Your Majesty.

176
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,919
How did I treat Consort Li in the past?

177
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,519
Your Majesty,

178
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,919
Prince Mo has ordered us
not to say a word about Consort Li.

179
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,879
How dare you!

180
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,759
Do you take orders
from him instead of me?

181
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,679
I wouldn't dare.

182
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:57,799
Consort Li was a woman you brought back

183
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,080
while traveling incognito.

184
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:02,200
You've always treated her
with great tenderness.

185
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,720
Not until later...

186
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,320
What happened to her?

187
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,759
Everyone who knew of this matter

188
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:09,879
was executed.

189
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,639
I only know

190
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,559
that she never returned to the palace

191
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,679
and has been missing ever since.

192
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,559
Consort Li...

193
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,120
My Lady,

194
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,639
you've been drinking so much!

195
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:28,559
Put this on.

196
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,480
I'm fine. I don't want it.

197
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:32,000
I don't think so.

198
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,720
I can see dark circles under your eyes!

199
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:39,039
Something's troubling me.

200
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,759
I can't fall asleep.

201
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,519
Why do you and Ling Xiao

202
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,240
have to make things so hard
on yourselves?

203
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,840
You wore yourself out

204
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,840
for his sake.

205
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,080
And he, to see you,

206
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,720
deliberately caught a cold.

207
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,240
What?

208
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:59,840
Did you say he got sick

209
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,879
just to see me?

210
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,919
Yeah.

211
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,679
To fool Mo Shuo,

212
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,559
he soaked himself in ice water all night

213
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:09,000
just to keep his date with you

214
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,840
and to spend the Qixi Festival together.

215
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,240
Then why would Mo Shuo put a curfew

216
00:11:12,519 --> 00:11:13,480
to stop him from going out?

217
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,759
Actually,

218
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,519
Ling Xiao shares the same experience
as you.

219
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:26,159
He fell off a cliff,

220
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,039
hit his head, and lost his memory.

221
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:30,480
For his safety, Mo Shuo

222
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:31,759
arranged some guards...

223
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,559
some servants to watch over him

224
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:35,759
and keep him from wandering off.

225
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,519
So that's how it is.

226
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,120
Whatever his past may be,

227
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,600
I've wronged him this time.

228
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,039
Where are you going?

229
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
Come back!

230
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:54,039
Jing Liuli.

231
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,679
Mu Ruyi.

232
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,519
Liu Rushi.

233
00:12:15,279 --> 00:12:18,639
How can three people look so alike?
